===Etymology===
From ''[[slip]]''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A person who slips, has slipped, or is currently slipping.
#A low [[shoe]] that can be slipped on and off easily and is usually worn indoors.
#:''Get out of bed, put on your '''slippers''', and come downstairs.''

